: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayU Money Payment Gateway for trip booking by setting up PayU Money Account with key details - <\\/span><b>Merchant Key and Merchant Salt.<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayU Money Payment Gateway, the payment page opens as a pop-up on your website which is a completely redirection less payment experience.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This payment gateway gives your customers a seamless checkout experience that keeps them in the framework of your website throughout the booking process and enables them to use their Credit\\/Debit card to pay without sharing any sensitive information.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Payment Gateway supports the payment modes such as Credit Card, Debit Card and only accepts payment in Indian Rupee (INR) currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/developer.payumoney.com\\/bolt-checkout\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Checkout page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Note: <\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Money Payment Gateway works only in India with Indian Rupee (INR) currency.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"30815,30816\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayU Money Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trips and tour payments via one of the leading financial services from India, PayU Money.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayU-payment-gateway.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 30754,\n                \"slug\": \"payhere-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayHere Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2020-02-06 15:49:00\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-02-06 17:17:38\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=30754\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere Payment Gateway is an extension for the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via one of Sri Lanka\\u2019s popular merchant services, PayHere.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayHere booking system for trip booking by setting up PayHere Account with key details \\u2013 <strong>Payment Merchant ID and PayHere Merchant Secret<\\/strong>.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayHere Payment Gateway, they are redirected to your merchant account on PayHere where they are requested to login and make the payment. PayHere handles the payments and redirects the traveler back to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayHere support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere is a payment processing service for any businesses to conveniently accept online payments locally or globally from customers all around the world. It connects local and international buyers and sellers on a single platform with multiple ways to pay.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere allows you to accept all local and global payment methods available in Sri Lanka through a single Online Payment Solution. You have everything under one roof with this payment gateway.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Payment from any country can be accepted, as long as you have a Sampath account under your business and use LKR, USD, GBP, EUR, and AUD as the transaction currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.payhere.lk\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayHere Global Page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-Settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30771\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-Settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"980\\\" height=\\\"833\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"30772,30773\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayHere Payment Gateway is an extension for the WP Travel Engine that allows tour operators to accept trips and tour payments via one of Sri Lanka\\u2019s popular merchant services, PayHere.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/02\\/PayHere-payment-gateway.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 22896,\n                \"slug\": \"trips-embedder\",\n                \"title\": \"Trips Embedder\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-11-07 08:33:04\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-21 14:54:04\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=22896\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder is an addon for WP Travel Engine that lets you quickly add\\/embed selected trips in between your blog posts and website pages content area, right from the WordPress WYSIWYG content editor.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the addon, you can easily display the details of your trip in grid or list format right in between posts or page contents, giving your readers easier access to related trip details.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon adds an additional button to your posts and page content editor, that pops open an easy UI to choose and display your desired trips.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22921\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1094\\\" height=\\\"325\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22945\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1323\\\" height=\\\"862\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The embedded trips are then shown right in-between your posts\\/page content to the visitors. Visitors can easily view the trips in the grid ( with carousel ) or list layout and access to get more details of the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Grid Layout<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22925\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"985\\\" height=\\\"559\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>List Layout<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22926\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"973\\\" height=\\\"496\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon also introduces <\\/span><b>new exciting Gutenberg Blocks<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> for WP Travel Engine plugin. You can now insert your trips in a list or grid with ease even with the new WordPress Gutenberg Editor.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery size=\\\"full\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" link=\\\"none\\\" ids=\\\"22930,22933\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Blogs and information pages play a vital role in Travel and Tour company business as they are the gateway for potential travelers seeking information\\/suggestions through your website. Blog articles are also a good source of information that potential travelers seek out.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon lets you easily embed your trips in your blog articles and pages. Having the list of your recommended trips in a concise list or grid layout lets the readers have a glance at related trips right while reading the content and helps in better conversion towards the trips.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective UI<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with no additional configurations required. After installing and activating the addon, new content editor button and Gutenberg Blocks are available to use and embed your trips to new and old blog posts and pages easily as per your requirements.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Embedder layout options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon provides two different layouts to display your selected trips. A grid layout, with a carousel and list layout, can be chosen as per your requirements. Both layouts are concise and effective to show maximum information about trips chosen to display.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22940\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"918\\\" height=\\\"524\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Number of posts options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon provides lets you decide how many trips to display in a single embed with an easy user interface. You can also choose no. of trips to display from your desired destinations, activities or trip type.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/postsnumber.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23036\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/postsnumber.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"703\\\" height=\\\"652\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Gutenberg Blocks<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Two different Gutenberg blocks are added in the Trips embedder addon that adds extra flexibility for the users using new WordPress Gutenberg Editor for posts and page content creation. New blocks take advantage of the powerful ReactJS based UI for seamless usability with WordPress Gutenberg blocks.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">External Embeds<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It\\u2019s super easy to embed trips from your site into your or your affiliate\\u2019s external website. To embed trips into any page, place the given HTML into the content area. Trips Embedder will automatically generate an Iframe and display your selected trips in the front end. The external website should not necessarily have WordPress installation or WP Travel Engine and its add-ons installed.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/12\\/trips-embedder.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-25664\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/12\\/trips-embedder.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"945\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update.<\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trips Embedder lets you quickly add\\/embed selected trips in between your blog posts and website pages content area, right from the WordPress WYSIWYG content editor. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/trips-embedder-banner.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20573,\n                \"slug\": \"extra-services\",\n                \"title\": \"Extra Services\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-10-22 08:08:01\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-15 17:43:35\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20573\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Extra Services is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to add <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">additional services for trips<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. The add-on makes it easier for the tour operators to add <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">services like airport pick-up, hotel drop-off, vehicle rental, or any other services you want to the trips.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The tour operators and travel agencies can specify the extra services and their rates while creating the package. Later, travelers can book the package along with extra services at a specified additional cost.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Extra Services can be both created globally or applied to each trip individually.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can add a service title, description, and price that the traveler can select on per traveler or on a per unit basis.\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21675\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"909\\\" height=\\\"898\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services1.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21676\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"946\\\" height=\\\"869\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services2.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21677\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"355\\\" height=\\\"822\\\" \\/><\\/a>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Extra Services makes it easier for the tour operators to add services like airport pick-up, hotel drop-off, vehicle rental, or any other services you want to the trips.\\u00a0\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/10\\/extra-services.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.3\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20468,\n                \"slug\": \"user-history\",\n                \"title\": \"User History\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-09-27 07:26:07\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-11-12 10:08:52\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20468\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">User History is a simple and effective addon that lets WP Travel Engine plugin users track and store browsing history of customers before bookings and enquiries are sent. With the lightweight addon, site admins can track the exact path and pages customers visited before actually making booking or enquiry.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The add-on gives you the desired insights on how customers are visiting your website, information on the referral link and the exact path followed before actually making booking and enquiry request. When a booking or enquiry is made from your website, you can view a piece of additional information regarding the customer browsing history along with the booking\\/enquiry details.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/history.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20544 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/history.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1429\\\" height=\\\"384\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As a travel\\/tour operator or agency it is very important to get the information on how customers are visiting your website. The information is very helpful to learn about the overall site\\u2019s browsing information. Site admins can easily see and analyze the information to get better conversion rates for bookings and enquiries.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Along with the details on URLs visited, the addon also gathers and displays information on how long the customer visited each page before making the request.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with minimal configurations required. You just need to install and activate the plugin on your site, the rest of the work will be handled by the addon automatically. Without any additional configurations, start getting the browsing history information on the site admin dashboard for every booking and enquiry requests made afterward.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get time elapsed information<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get automatically calculated time duration for each page visited by users, also the information on total timespan customer stayed on your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/elapsed.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20545 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/elapsed.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1438\\\" height=\\\"437\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Referral link information<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get information about your site\\u2019s traffic. With WP Travel Engine user history addon, you can easily view the information of the referral link from where customer visited your site. The details will help you in analytics and preparing marketing strategies for your travel business.<\\/span>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Get user history in booking emails<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">With the new {user_history} email tag, you can now choose to get the user history details in your booking email notification also. See all of the browsing history details from the customers right in the booking notification email on the go.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/booking-history.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20546 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/booking-history.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1600\\\" height=\\\"819\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cookie consent information<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon also provides an additional cookie consent information which site admins can easily enable, configure and edit. As user history tracking depends on the use of cookies, you can easily inform your customers about your cookie policies.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-20527 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/cookie-consent.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"402\\\" height=\\\"216\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Gravity forms support<\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine user history addon extends support with Gravity Forms, one of the most popular forms plugin in WordPress. With the support site admins can get all the information and benefits of user history addon even while using Gravity forms form for booking\\/enquiries right in the entry details screen.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20547 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/GF-Support.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1589\\\" height=\\\"846\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can choose individually each of the gravity forms form in your site you want to track and save user history information.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you are using Gravity Forms plugin in your website, Gravity forms selection settings for user history is available in <\\/span><b>Admin Dashboard &gt; Trips &gt; Settings &gt; Extensions &gt; User History Settings &gt; Gravity form(s) to capture user history<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-20560 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/Select-GF.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1347\\\" height=\\\"525\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Continuous Development &amp; support<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Like all of our addons, we provide dedicated support for any help required for using the addon. You can simply drop us a support message, feature request or any queries regarding the addon and get a prompt response.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are also working on continuous development and adding exciting new features to the addon with each update. <\\/span>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"WP Travel Engine user history addon is a simple and effective addon that lets WP Travel Engine plugin users track and store browsing history of customers before bookings and enquiries are sent.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/user-story.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 20311,\n                \"slug\": \"himalayan-bank-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2019-09-24 09:02:06\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-02-28 16:37:28\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=20311\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of the leading banks in Nepal, Himalayan Bank.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies in Nepal can enable the Himalayan Bank Payment gateway for trip booking by setting up Himalayan Account with key details \\u2013 <\\/span><b>Merchant ID<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><b>Secret Key<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway, the traveler is taken to Himalayan Bank to make a secure payment. After payment, the trip booking is confirmed and the traveler is redirected to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">For redirection, you should ask Himalayan Bank to set the <\\/span><b>Backend-URL<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><b>Frontend-URL<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> of your site on their server. Backend-URL is the URL where you get the response of your payment from the server and the Frontend-URL is the URL where the payer is redirected after successful payment is made.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway incorporates Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Union Pay cards and accepts payment in Nepali(NPR) and US currency. This results in increased conversion rates, improved customer experience and access to the global market.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Note:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway works in Nepal with Nepali and US currency only.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway works on the WordPress site and ONLY with <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel\\u00a0 Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> plugin.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"20312,20316,20313\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Himalayan Bank Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of the leading banks in Nepal, Himalayan Bank.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/09\\/himalayan-payment-gateway-1000x683.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"49.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 7093,\n                \"slug\": \"paypal-express-checkout-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayPal Express Checkout Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-12-28 08:19:51\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-15 17:38:18\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=7093\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Express Checkout Payment Gateway is an extension for <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments through PayPal Express. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayPal Express Checkout system for trip booking by setting up PayPal Express Account with key details - <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Client ID <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">and <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Secret<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler is ready to checkout with their PayPal account, they simply have to click the PayPal Checkout button which will redirect them to a PayPal checkout page. All billing and customer details are completed on the PayPal Express checkout page before the traveler is redirected back to your travel website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayPal Express support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayPal Express is available in most countries. <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">To know if your country is supported, please see the <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">complete <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/developer.paypal.com\\/docs\\/classic\\/api\\/country_codes\\/#countries-supported-in-paypal-payments\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">list here<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Do PayPal Express require my site to have an SSL certificate?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">An SSL certificate is not required for PayPal Express, though it is highly recommended.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"7094,7095\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayPal Express Checkout Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments through PayPal Express.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/12\\/Paypal-Express.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                 