avelengine.com\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> plugin to add a weather forecast widget to the desired trips.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Weather Forecast allows users to select their preferred weather location from over 800,000 locations around the globe. The widget displays weather conditions like current temperature, feels like temperature, wind, humidity, pressure, and UV index along with the sunrise\\/sunset time for the location. It also supports Hourly forecast and Daily forecast along with the weather condition icons.<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\r\\n<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"6728,6735,6726\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Weather Forecast is an extension for WP Travel Engine plugin to add a weather forecast widget to the desired trips.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/12\\/trip-weather-forecast-banner.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"19.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"49.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"69.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 6695,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-fixed-starting-dates-countdown\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Fixed Starting Dates Countdown\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-12-14 04:46:51\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-10-14 10:46:36\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=6695\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Fixed Starting Dates Countdown is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> plugin to add a fixed starting dates countdown to desired trips. It is dependent on the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-fixed-starting-dates\\/\\\">Trip Fixed Starting Dates<\\/a> add-on.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Fixed Starting Dates Countdown adds a Trip Starting Countdown widget in the widgets section and a Trip Countdown Configuration meta box in the trip dashboard. It is dependent on Trip Fixed Starting Dates addon causing it to work only on the trips that have Fixed Starting Dates configured.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">One must choose a Fixed Starting Trip date from the drop-down on the individual trip post, else the countdown will automatically begin from the next upcoming Fixed Starting Trip Date.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Screenshots<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"1\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"6698,6697,6696\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Fixed Starting Dates Countdown adds a Trip Starting Countdown widget in the widgets section and a Trip Countdown Configuration meta box in the trip dashboard. It is dependent on Trip Fixed Starting Dates add-on causing it to work only on the trips that have Fixed Starting Dates configured.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/12\\/fixed-starting-dates-countdown-banner.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"19.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"49.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"69.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 2079,\n                \"slug\": \"essential-add-ons-bundle\",\n                \"title\": \"Essential Add-ons Bundle\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-08-14 05:16:08\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-06 06:49:31\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=2079\",\n                \"content\": \"Essential Add-ons Bundle is a package of <b>four<\\/b> premium WP Travel Engine \\u00a0extensions that you can get in a single purchase. With this Essential Add-ons Bundle, you will get four premium extensions covering everything from advanced trip search to trip reviews.\\r\\n<h2>Essential Add-ons Bundle includes the following extensions:<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2>1. Trip Fixed Starting Dates<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-fixed-starting-dates\\/\\\">Trip Fixed Starting Dates<\\/a> allows a tour operator or a travel agency to show trip fixed starting dates and number of space available for booking.\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1864\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Fixed-Starting-Dates-1024x683.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"514\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>2. Trip Search<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-search\\/\\\">Trip Search<\\/a> provides a one-step trip search engine to search trips by Destination, Activities, Duration, and Budget on your travel website.\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1786\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-1-1024x683.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"514\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>3. Trip Reviews<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-reviews\\/\\\">Trip Reviews<\\/a> allows a tour operator or a travel agency to add authentic trip reviews onto their website.\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2119\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/08\\/Trip-Review-1024x768.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"578\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h2>4. Group Discount<\\/h2>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/group-discount\\/\\\">Group Discount<\\/a> allows a tour operator or a travel agency to enable group discounts in their trip packages.\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1863\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Group-Discount-1024x683.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"770\\\" height=\\\"514\\\" \\/>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Essential Add-ons Bundle is a package of four premium WP Travel Engine  extensions that you can get in a single purchase. With this Essential Add-ons Bundle, you will get four premium extensions covering everything from advanced trip search to trip reviews.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/02\\/Plugin-Bundle-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 14,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-ons Bundle\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons-bundle\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 14,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_tag\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 1,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ]\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"89.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"199.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"249.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 2107,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-reviews\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Reviews\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-08-08 11:31:49\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-12-26 17:35:34\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=2107\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows a tour operator or a travel agency to add authentic trip reviews onto their website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews extension adds a Trip Reviews sub-menu and a Review Tab on activation. Travel agency or tour operators (admins) can add reviews from both the Trip Reviews sub-menu and Review Tab, while travelers (users) can add reviews to the individual trips from the Review Tab in the frontend. Admin can later approve or unapprove the reviews. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can also list all the reviews in tabs or trip content using the shortcode <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">- <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">[Wte_Trip_Review_List]<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews helps you get more trip bookings with social proof. It calculates the average ratings for a trip based on the total number of reviews. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Reviews is SEO optimized. The reviews rich snippet is shown in search engines which increases Click Through Rate (CTR), and therefore, helps to improve search engine ranking. It also encourages your travelers to leave reviews and in turn increase conversion of your travel agency.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Screenshots<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"2111,2113,2118,2110,2112\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Reviews is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows a tour operator or a travel agency to add authentic trip reviews onto their website.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/08\\/Trip-Review.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.6\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1750,\n                \"slug\": \"partial-payment\",\n                \"title\": \"Partial Payment\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 09:02:55\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-08-06 06:51:16\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1750\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Partial Payment is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a>. Partial Payment makes it easier for the travelers to book for a trip or tour package in an installment payment basis. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The tour operators and travel agencies can specify the partial payment rate of the trip in percentage or amount while creating the package. Later, travelers can book the package at a specified installment cost. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When using Partial Payment with WP Travel Engine, the travelers can view the Total Remaining Payment and Deposit Payable Amount in the checkout page. This results in a better user experience and increases in sales or conversion.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Partial Payment can be applied to each trip individually.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour Operators and Agencies can choose whether to specify the Partial Payment rate in Percentage or in Amount. <\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Partial Payment in Percentage:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> The partial payment amount of the trip price <\\/span><b>in percentage<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to be paid while booking the trip. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Partial Payment in Amount:<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> \\u00a0The partial payment amount of the trip price <\\/span><b>in figures<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> to be paid while booking the trip.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1753\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Screenshot_2018-07-16-WP-Travel-Engine-Admin-Settings-\\u2039-wptravelengine-test-Blog-\\u2014-WordPress-300x148.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"566\\\" height=\\\"279\\\" \\/><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1754\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/CHECKOUT-\\u2013-wptravelengine-test-Blog--300x139.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"563\\\" height=\\\"261\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Partial Payment is an extension for WP Travel Engine. Partial Payment makes it easier for the travelers to book for a trip or tour package in an installment payment basis.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Partial-Payment-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"19.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"49.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"69.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.4\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1757,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-search\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Search\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 08:10:21\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2019-12-24 14:42:58\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1757\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that provides a one-step trip search engine to search trips by Destination, Activities, Duration, and Budget on your travel website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/downloads\\/trip-fixed-starting-dates\\/\\\"><b>Fixed Trip Starting Dates<\\/b><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> is another extension for WP Travel Engine that adds Fixed Starting Dates for a trip. If the add-on is added, then trip can also be searched according to the Trip Starting Dates.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search indexes all the trip posts and adds destination, activity, duration, budget, and trip starting dates as search filters in a drop down. <\\/span>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Destination<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - User can search for trips by Destination such as Pokhara, Mustang, etc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Activities<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - User can search for trips by Activities such as Paragliding, Rafting, etc.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Duration<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - User can search for trips by Duration such as 5 days, 10 days.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Budget<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - User can search for trips by the Budget range. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><b>Search by Trip Starting Dates<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> - User can search for trips by Trip Starting Dates. <\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search extension also allows you to choose which filters (destination, activity, duration, budget) to exclude from the search.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trip Search is a very good solution for tour operators and travel agencies to increase user experience and sales or conversion.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1758\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/search-300x38.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"576\\\" height=\\\"73\\\" \\/> <img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1759\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-Result-\\u2013-Travel-Agency-Pro-224x300.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"480\\\" height=\\\"643\\\" \\/> <img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1760\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/hidesearch-300x148.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"582\\\" height=\\\"287\\\" \\/>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Trip Search is an extension for WP Travel Engine that provides a one-step trip search engine to search trips by Destination, Activities, Duration, and Budget on your travel website. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Trip-Search-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.1.6\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1744,\n                \"slug\": \"payfast-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayFast Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-20 08:07:19\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-21 14:15:16\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1744\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast Payment Gateway is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of South Africa\\u2019s popular merchant service, PayFast. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayFast booking system for trip booking by setting up PayFast Account with key details - Merchant Key and Merchant ID. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayFast Payment Gateway, they are redirected to your merchant account on PayFast where they are requested to login and make the payment. PayFast handles the payments and redirects the traveler back to your website. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<b>Which countries does PayFast support?<\\/b>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast is a payment processing service for South Africa. It connects local and international buyers and sellers on a single platform with multiple ways to pay. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Payment from any country can be accepted, as long as you use ZAR as the currency. To know more about how does it work, please visit the <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.payfast.co.za\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayFast Global Page<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/01\\/Payfast-settings.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-29429 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2020\\/01\\/Payfast-settings.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"872\\\" height=\\\"827\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1747\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayFast-Engine-Payment-Methods-300x114.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"703\\\" height=\\\"267\\\" \\/>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayFast Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of South Africa\\u2019s popular merchant service, PayFast. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayFast.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.4\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 1055,\n                \"slug\": \"payu-biz-payment-gateway\",\n                \"title\": \"PayU Biz Payment Gateway\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-07-19 08:55:50\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-02-10 11:36:01\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=1055\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Payment Gateway is an extension for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wordpress.org\\/plugins\\/wp-travel-engine\\/\\\">WP Travel Engine<\\/a> that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of leading financial services in global growth markets, PayU. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tour operators and travel agencies can enable the PayU Payment gateway for trip booking by setting up PayU Account with key details - Merchant Key and Merchant Salt. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a traveler books a trip via PayU Payment Gateway, the traveler is taken to PayU to make a secure payment. No SSL certificate is required on your site. After payment, the trip booking is confirmed and the traveler is redirected to your website.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">PayU Payment Gateway incorporates payment methods like Credit Card, Debit Card, Internet Banking, and PayPal. The travelers can make card payments as well as direct payments via any of the associated banks. This results in increased conversion rates, improved customer experience and access to the global market.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1741\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Screenshot_2018-07-16-PayUbiz-300x283.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"563\\\" height=\\\"532\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img class=\\\"alignnone wp-image-1742\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/WP-Travel-Engine-Admin-Settings-\\u2039-wptravelengine-PayU-300x189.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"514\\\" height=\\\"324\\\" \\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"PayU Payment Gateway is an extension for WP Travel Engine that allows you to accept trip and tour payments via one of leading financial services in global growth markets, PayU. \",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/PayU-1.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\