ripe Payment Gateway extension allows you to accept credit cards directly on your website through <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/\\\">Stripe.com<\\/a>\\u00a0account.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen using Stripe payment gateway with WP Travel Engine, the travelers enter their credit card details on the checkout page and never leave your site. This results in better user experience and increases in sales or conversion.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Which countries does Stripe support?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nStripe is currently available in many countries. It is also constantly expanding to more countries. \\u00a0To know if your country is supported, please visit the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/global\\\">Stripe Global page<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Does Stripe require my site to have an SSL certificate?<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nYes, you will need to use SSL certificate with Stripe. The pages that include a payment form should be prefixed with <i>https:\\/\\/<\\/i>. For more information, please visit <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/stripe.com\\/docs\\/security\\\">Stripe Security page<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery link=\\\"file\\\" size=\\\"large\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" ids=\\\"566,565,564\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This Stripe Payment Gateway extension allows you to accept credit cards directly on your website through Stripe.com account.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/07\\/Stripe-Payment.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 6,\n                        \"name\": \"Payment Gateways\",\n                        \"slug\": \"payment-gateways\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 6,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 5,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.0.6\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 146,\n                \"slug\": \"group-discount\",\n                \"title\": \"Group Discount\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-15 13:17:44\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-29 18:21:06\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=146\",\n                \"content\": \"<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to give adult as well as child group discount to their customers. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Giving a group discount is a great way to increase the conversation rate and the number of booking. <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a trip includes group discount allowing a customer to book for multiple people, the customer can immediately book the trip.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Imagine you run a trip and offer an adult and child group discount for the trip. The cost of the trip per person is $1000. To increase the number of booking, you want to give the discount as follows: <\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><b>Number of Travelers<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><b>Cost Per Traveller ($)<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><b>Total Cost ($)<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1000<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1000<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">2<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">900<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1800<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">3<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">800<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">2400<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><b>Number of Child Travelers<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><b>Cost Per Child Traveller ($)<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><b>Total Cost ($)<\\/b><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">600<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">600<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">2<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">500<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1000<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">3<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">400<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">1200<\\/span><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">You can easily provide a group discount using this extension.<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Group discount can be added to each trip individually. \\u00a0<\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery size=\\\"full\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" ids=\\\"6875,6876,6884\\\"]\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to give group discount to their customers.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2018\\/12\\/group-discount-new.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 5,\n                        \"name\": \"Add-Ons\",\n                        \"slug\": \"add-ons\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 5,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 22,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"singlesite\": \"39.00\",\n                \"2-5sites\": \"79.00\",\n                \"unlimitedsites\": \"99.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.1.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"years\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"1\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 79,\n                \"slug\": \"trip-fixed-starting-dates\",\n                \"title\": \"Trip Fixed Starting Dates\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-01-10 11:38:32\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2020-01-29 12:04:38\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/?post_type=download&p=79\",\n                \"content\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to show trip fixed starting dates and number of space available for booking.\\r\\n\\r\\nFor example, you may have fixed dates for a trip and only limited seats are available for the date. Then using this extension, you can added the dates and number of seats available for the dates. Booking can only be made on those dates. After a booking is made, the number of available space automatically get reduced.\\r\\n\\r\\n[gallery columns=\\\"2\\\" size=\\\"medium\\\" link=\\\"file\\\" ids=\\\"18194,18192,18191,96,18193\\\"]\\r\\n<h2>Features<\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Trip Starting Dates (Fixed Departure Dates)<\\/strong>: You can add unlimited trip starting dates for every trips.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Space\\/Seat Available:<\\/strong> You can add number of space or seat available for every trip starting dates.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Automatically Reduce Space\\/Seat:<\\/strong> When a booking is made on a fixed trip starting date, the number of seats automatically get reduced based on number of space booked. For example, if there were 10 space available and 5 people booked on a date, then now the number of available space displayed is just 5.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Past Dates Removal:<\\/strong> Past trip dates are automatically removed. For example, if you have a trip starting date on 20th January 2018, then it is no longer displayed on 21st January 2017 because the date has already passed.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li><strong>Short Codes:<\\/strong> You can change the position where the fixed starting dates are displayed using the short codes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"This extension allows travel agencies and tour operators to show trip fixed starting dates and number of space available for booking.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/08\\/Trip-F